channel.title: How can I put an Npc on an Interface?
channel.description:
How to put Npc on an interface ?
I want to know that because I'm doing my Thieving Interface for my server. When you click on the Thieving skill, an interface will appear and it will say the npc needed for certain level to pickpocket. I tried to put them on an interface like man and hero and others but when I compile and run my server, I get anything for the npc.
I did this tutorial: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,384716.0.html It works perfectly with items but I tried with npc and it doesn't work.
Can anyone help me ? Thanks
